thing now, and your later life, the main thing that 
I don't like about is they tell me right now, we're

44:11.718 --> 44:28.604
getting off subject, but this is something I feel 
strong about. Right now, I cannot make more than

44:28.624 --> 44:37.377
$463 a month, or they'll take money away from me. 
