44:40.945 --> 44:43.629
Where's the incentive? They say when you get 72, 
you make all the money you want to. It's basically

44:47.816 --> 44:50.481
wrong, the concept of it. To pay,

44:50.501 --> 44:59.155
well, in effect, if you will, you can do it paying 
people not to work. And no wonder there is graft in

44:59.175 --> 45:02.059
it. No wonder it opens the field for People who 
don't have the so-called people of the minority,

45:07.473 --> 45:19.088
if you will, and the culture of some of them. No 
wonder. Well, we're all going to get back now. I

